{"tid":445022,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人去過大阪櫻花主場睇波？","createTime":"2017-10-23T04:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T07:55:51.000Z","uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7a79e8e0f3802ba8cc1f06db60ab628ee68213","tid":445022,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"大長居球場 姐係靚d 大d yanmar 冠名那個<br />\n<br />\nCat 4 係正中間 3700 Yen<br />\n 但點解同樣都係邊線看台 對面既就劃成cat 2 cat 1 咁咁多？？？<br />\n<br />\nCat 4 最正中d 短係唔係基本上買唔到 買到既都係比最側邊你？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i64.tinypic.com/ofc30m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi64.tinypic.com%2Fofc30m.jpg&h=6fe5f6d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11b0dbc6035201691c5b5277c732370b0faf7019","tid":445022,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:15:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"552c05150436b7e5cb51c3c24b55b5989794c847","tid":445022,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"去過但答唔到你要既答案，不過幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676155f978ec6c98ede996dbf0b319b1c5ac7ff9","tid":445022,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:19:49.000Z","msg":"樓主試下去日職post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有位叫吉田董既手足話唔定幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36739c98e5804143d18e60fae0ae708abd37559","tid":445022,"uid":99175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:20:44.000Z","msg":"後備席 出場 教練 訪問"},{"pid":"ecbc0da0c21edb2931332f54efde95539d14d8eb","tid":445022,"uid":99175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後備席 出場 教練 訪問</blockquote><br />\n所以中間貴d 加埋上一層就係媒體用 2邊其實唔係好睇到我覺得 睇到眼都花埋"},{"pid":"2c875c4e04882cb437b59af3cc4028902c1af5c6","tid":445022,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>後備席 出場 教練 訪問</blockquote><br />\n所以中間貴d 加埋上一層就係媒體用 2邊其實唔係好睇到我覺得 睇到眼都花埋</blockquote><br />\n呢樣合理 但點解同樣係中間<br />\nback stand 全部中間低層都係cat4<br />\n但main stand 就分3 2 1 (全部貴過4), 最中間既位仲要係白色無得買 (留哂比貴票同vip?)"},{"pid":"df7fbff4e03168354078a158d638d776ac02e4b9","tid":445022,"uid":8122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/23/192649_13ee6a5c1ef6d7a4b5712158730ca002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2F192649_13ee6a5c1ef6d7a4b5712158730ca002.jpg&h=79614755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為對面係記者, 高層坐既位<br />\n唔會拎出黎賣飛"},{"pid":"6311a229be41f8ec074364db41206a22863458c8","tid":445022,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"買黃色果區最好"},{"pid":"bb9572f6f40410953c10d99495658d6f27824ebb","tid":445022,"uid":10313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"買HOME自由席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5626fd8a8ea4629bf555260f8cf3f74d8da293cb","tid":445022,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買HOME自由席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪即係黃色果區"},{"pid":"1b8c554db93db5d17a24b03c13e63cc85c6247ea","tid":445022,"uid":10313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買HOME自由席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪即係黃色果區</blockquote><br />\n粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6958dd9d506b608e12b4452cec0cca1b1939c62e","tid":445022,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eserv